{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"62feac0a66","title":"部分人认为堵后门有八个“不好办”","origin":"美国图书馆收藏","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e69941a46a","index":0,"year":1961,"month":11,"day":17,"articleId":"62feac0a66"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5026376ea5","name":"辽宁"},{"id":"b4842e1551","name":"新华通讯社"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"84b6224583","type":"title","text":"部分人认为堵后门有八个“不好办”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"62feac0a66"},{"id":"087855ffc0","type":"authors","text":"新华通讯社辽宁","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"62feac0a66"},{"id":"c0f34f5c49","type":"paragraph","text":"本刊讯  据最近辽宁省委召开的反“走后门”工作会议上反映，某些人认为堵后门有八个“不好办”。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"62feac0a66"},{"id":"76a35e10aa","type":"paragraph","text":"一、生产厂长说：“不浇油，不转轴，不给点好处，原料弄不来，设计不出来，运输不进来，安装不起来，生产不出来。不走后门影响生产，不好办！”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"62feac0a66"},{"id":"a640f7ef23","type":"paragraph","text":"二、福利厂长说：“不叫以物易物，职工没菜吃，揭不开锅，生活安排不下去，不好办！”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"62feac0a66"},{"id":"db61da94a5","type":"paragraph","text":"三、生产队长说：“国家不给化肥，还不让自己换，怎能发展生产？不好办！”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"62feac0a66"},{"id":"bb2b629c96","type":"paragraph","text":"四、公社干部说：“厂社挂勾讲协作，不能一头热，堵死后门影响关系，不好办！”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"62feac0a66"},{"id":"1efc04ddcd","type":"paragraph","text":"五、商业部门说：“开后门，好办事，不开点后门运输关过不去，汽车司机都搪不了，得罪了司机不好办！”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"62feac0a66"},{"id":"e51052ba24","type":"paragraph","text":"六、职工干部说：“要遵守纪律不许排队，最后买又没有了，不让走后门，就得啥不买，啥不用，不好办！”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"62feac0a66"},{"id":"5e88679181","type":"paragraph","text":"七、副食供应部门说：“调拨的物资少，和市场需要相差太悬殊，供应不上，飞行员上不了天，高温不能作业，只好拿东西换，不让以物易物，不好办！”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"62feac0a66"},{"id":"76d5234ee7","type":"paragraph","text":"八、商店经理说：“领导干部来叩后门，不开不好办！”","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"62feac0a66"},{"id":"09a0a222e1","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：1961年11月17日新华社《简讯》。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"62feac0a66"}],"page":{"id":"4430aa32a2","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"62feac0a66","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}